<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77681f8b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410aaa–45"><num value="410aaa–45">§ 410aaa–45.</num><heading> Abolishment of scenic area</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The East Mojave National Scenic Area, designated on <date date="1981-01-13">January 13, 1981</date> (46 FR 3994), and modified on <date date="1983-08-09">August 9, 1983</date> (48 FR 36210), is hereby abolished.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77681f8c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/433/tV/s505">Pub. L. 103–433, title V, § 505</ref>, <date date="1994-10-31">Oct. 31, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/4490">108 Stat. 4490</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
